				-
			-
				Surah 7 - The Heights: Ayah 114
			-
				-
					He said, "Yes, and you will be among my favorites."
				-
			-
				Surah 7 - The Heights: Ayah 115
			-
				-
					They said, "Moses! Either you throw, or we are the ones to throw."
				-
			-
				Surah 7 - The Heights: Ayah 116
			-
				-
