				-
			-
				Surah 7 - The Heights: Ayah 118
			-
				-
					So the truth came to pass, and what they were producing came to nothing.
				-
			-
				Surah 7 - The Heights: Ayah 119
			-
				-
					There they were defeated, and utterly reduced.
				-
			-
				Surah 7 - The Heights: Ayah 120
			-
				-
					And the magicians fell to their knees.
				-
			-
				Surah 7 - The Heights: Ayah 121
			-
				-
					They said, "We have believed in the Lord of the Worlds."
				-
