		-
			Surah 9 - The Repentance
		-
			-
				Surah 9 - The Repentance: Ayah 1
			-
				-
					A declaration of immunity from God and His Messenger to the polytheists with
					whom you had made a treaty.
				-
			-
				Surah 9 - The Repentance: Ayah 2
			-
				-
					So travel the land for four months, and know that you cannot escape God, and
					that God will disgrace the disbelievers.
				-
			-
				Surah 9 - The Repentance: Ayah 3
			-
				-
