				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 19
			-
				-
					We unleashed upon them a screaming wind, on a day of unrelenting misery.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 20
			-
				-
					Plucking the people away, as though they were trunks of uprooted palm-trees.
