					Thamood rejected the warnings.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 24
			-
				-
					They said, "Are we to follow one of us, a human being? We would then go astray,
					and end up in Hell.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 25
			-
				-
					Was the message given to him, out of all of us? In fact, he is a wicked liar."
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 26
			-
				-
					They will know tomorrow who the wicked liar is.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 27
			-
				-
					We are sending the she-camel as a test for them; so watch them and be patient.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 28
			-
				-
					And inform them that the water is to be shared between them; each share of
					drink made available.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 29
			-
				-
					But they called their friend, and he dared, and he slaughtered.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 30
			-
				-
					So how were My punishment and My warnings?
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 31
			-
				-
					We sent against them a single Scream, and they became like crushed hay.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 32
			-
				-
					We made the Quran easy to understand. Is there anyone who would understand?
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 33
			-
				-
					The people of Lot rejected the warnings.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 34
			-
				-
					We unleashed upon them a shower of stones, except for the family of Lot; We
					rescued them at dawn.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 35
			-
				-
					A blessing from Us. Thus We reward the thankful.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 36
			-
				-
					He had warned them of Our onslaught, but they dismissed the warnings.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 37
			-
				-
					They even lusted for his guest, so We obliterated their eyes. "So taste My
					punishment and My warnings."
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 38
			-
				-
					Early morning brought upon them enduring punishment.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 39
			-
				-
					So taste My punishment and My warnings.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 40
			-
				-
					We made the Quran easy to memorize. Is there anyone who would memorize?
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 41
			-
				-
					The warnings also came to the people of Pharaoh.
				-
			-
				Surah 54 - The Moon: Ayah 42
			-
				-
