			Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth
		-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 0
			-
				-
					In the name of God, the Gracious, the Merciful.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 1
			-
				-
					By those who snatch violently.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 2
			-
				-
					And those who remove gently.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 3
			-
				-
					And those who glide smoothly.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 4
			-
				-
					And those who race swiftly.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 5
			-
				-
					And those who regulate events.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 6
			-
				-
					On the Day when the Quake quakes.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 7
			-
				-
					And is followed by the Successor.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 8
			-
				-
					Hearts on that Day will be pounding.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 9
			-
				-
					Their sights downcast.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 10
			-
				-
					They say, "Are we to be restored to the original condition?
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 11
			-
				-
					When we have become hollow bones?"
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 12
			-
				-
					They say, "This is a losing proposition."
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 13
			-
				-
					But it will be only a single nudge.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 14
			-
				-
					And they will be awake.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 15
			-
				-
					Has the story of Moses reached you?
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 16
			-
				-
					When His Lord called out to him in the sacred valley of Tuwa.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 17
			-
				-
					"Go to Pharaoh-he has transgressed."
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 18
			-
				-
					And say, "Do you care to be cleansed?
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 19
			-
				-
					And I will guide you to your Lord, and you will turn reverent."
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 20
			-
				-
					He showed him the Greatest Miracle.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 21
			-
				-
					But he denied and defied.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 22
			-
				-
					Then turned his back, and tried.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 23
			-
				-
					And gathered and proclaimed.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 24
			-
				-
					He said, "I am your Lord, the most high."
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 25
			-
				-
					So God seized him with an exemplary punishment, in the last and in the first.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 26
			-
				-
					In this is a lesson for whoever fears.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 27
			-
				-
					Are you more difficult to create, or the heaven? He constructed it.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 28
			-
				-
					He raised its masses, and proportioned it.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 29
			-
				-
					And He dimmed its night, and brought out its daylight.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 30
			-
				-
					And the earth after that He spread.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 31
			-
				-
					And from it, He produced its water and its pasture.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 32
			-
				-
					And the mountains, He anchored.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 33
			-
				-
					A source of enjoyment for you and for your animals.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 34
			-
				-
					But when the Great Cataclysm arrives.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 35
			-
				-
					A Day when man will remember what he has endeavored.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 36
			-
				-
					And Hell will be displayed to whoever sees.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 37
			-
				-
					As for him who was defiant.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 38
			-
				-
					And preferred the life of this world.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 39
			-
				-
					Then Hell is the shelter.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 40
			-
				-
					But as for him who feared the Standing of his Lord, and restrained the self
					from desires.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 41
			-
				-
					Then Paradise is the shelter.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 42
			-
				-
					They ask you about the Hour, "When will it take place?"
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 43
			-
				-
					You have no knowledge of it.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 44
			-
				-
					To your Lord is its finality.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 45
			-
				-
					You are just a warner for whoever dreads it.
				-
			-
				Surah 79 - Those Who Drag Forth: Ayah 46
			-
				-
					On the Day when they witness it-as though they only stayed an evening, or its
					morning.
