			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 9
			-
				-
					For what crime was she killed?
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 10
			-
				-
					When the records are made public.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 11
			-
				-
					When the sky is peeled away.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 12
			-
				-
					When the Fire is set ablaze.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 13
			-
				-
					When Paradise is brought near.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 14
			-
				-
					Each soul will know what it has readied.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 15
			-
				-
					I swear by the galaxies.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 16
			-
				-
					Precisely running their courses.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 17
			-
				-
					And by the night as it recedes.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 18
			-
				-
					And by the morn as it breathes.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 19
			-
				-
					This is the speech of a noble messenger.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 20
			-
				-
					Endowed with power, eminent with the Lord of the Throne.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 21
			-
				-
					Obeyed and honest.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 22
			-
				-
					Your friend is not possessed.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 23
			-
				-
					He saw him on the luminous horizon.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 24
			-
				-
					And He does not withhold knowledge of the Unseen.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 25
			-
				-
					And it is not the word of an accursed devil.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 26
			-
				-
					So where are you heading?
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 27
			-
				-
					It is only a Reminder to all mankind.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 28
			-
				-
					To whoever of you wills to go straight.
				-
			-
				Surah 81 - The Overthrowing: Ayah 29
			-
				-
					But you cannot will, unless God wills-The Lord of the Worlds.
