				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 8
			-
				-
					In whatever shape He willed, He assembled you.
				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 9
			-
				-
					But you reject the religion.
				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 10
			-
				-
					Though over you are watchers.
				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 11
			-
				-
					Honest recorders.
				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 12
			-
				-
					They know everything you do.
				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 13
			-
				-
					The virtuous will be in bliss.
				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 14
			-
				-
					While the wicked will be in Hell.
				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 15
			-
				-
					They will enter it on the Day of Justice.
				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 16
			-
				-
					And they will not be absent from it.
				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 17
			-
				-
					But what will convey to you what the Day of Justice is?
				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 18
			-
				-
					Then again, what will convey to you what the Day of Justice is?
				-
			-
				Surah 82 - The Cleaving: Ayah 19
			-
				-
					The Day when no soul will avail another soul anything; and the decision on that
					Day is God's.
